sequenceDiagram
    participant launchd
    participant Service
    participant RM as RuntimeManager
    participant Reg as SessionRegistry
    participant Tmux as TmuxRuntime

    launchd->>Service: start at login
    Service->>RM: initialize()
    RM->>Reg: load known sessions
    RM->>Tmux: discover()
    Tmux-->>RM: running tmux sessions
    RM->>Reg: reconcile statuses
    Service-->>launchd: running
